{8010}{}{The Terror Night is dead, Jeb.}
{8020}{}{How goes the town, Jeb? Is it safe again?}
{8030}{}{The Deathclaw is dead, Jeb. You can tell people not to worry so much anymore.}
{8040}{}{Okay, Jeb, I've got 50x pieces of Brahmin Meat to lure the Deathclaw into our trap! I spoke with a Trapper in Klamath, he told me everything that we needed to know.}
